            <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/nav_icon03.png\" alt=\"医療ガス\" class=\"nav-icon\">\n                        <p class=\"mega_text\">医療<span class=\"blue\">ガス</span></p>\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                      <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/service/industrial_equipment/\">\n                        <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/nav_icon05.png\" alt=\"関連機器・資材\" class=\"nav-icon\">\n                        <p class=\"mega_text\">関連機器・資材</p>\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                      <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/service/engineering/\">\n                        <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/nav_icon04.png\" alt=\"エンジニアリング\" class=\"nav-icon\">\n                        <p class=\"mega_text\">エンジニアリング</p>\n                      </a>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/about/\">会社概要</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/access/\">事業拠点</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/sdgs/\">SDGs</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/recruit/\"class=\"active\">採⽤情報</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/sitemap/\">サイトマップ</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCweUh5ZjpdtgK5POqmPTkyw\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/btn_youtube.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"btn_youtube\"></a></li>\n                                <li class=\"menu_contact\"><a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/otoiawase/captmail.cgi\"><i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i> CONTACT</a></li>\n                                </li>\n                <li class=\"menu_tel\"><a href=\"tel:019-638-2121\">019-638-2121</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n    \n    <main class=\"topBtn_box\">\n\n<div class=\"second_bg\"></div>\n<section class=\"second\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"topics_bg second\">\n      <h2 class=\"tit_topics tit_space\">\n        <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/tit_recruit.png\" alt=\"Recruit 採用情報\">\n      </h2>\n    </div>\n\n    <nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n        <li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com\">TOP</a></li>\n        <li class=\"breadcrumb-item active\" aria-current=\"page\">採用情報</li>\n      </ol>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- <article>\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-12 text-center\">\n          <p class=\"lead mb-4\">\n            直接目には見えませんが自動車や航空、船、紙、エネルギー燃料、発電、食品や飲料、農業、研究開発、衛生、医療など生活のあらゆるシーンで使われています。\n          </p>\n          <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/recruit_gas_map.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid mb-5\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </article> -->\n\n\n    <article>\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-9\">\n          <dl>\n            <dt class=\"qa_tit tit_space_s\">Ｑ：第一開明って何の会社なの？</dt>\n            <dd class=\"faq_dd\">昭和26年(1951年)に創業以来、産業用・医療用の各種高圧ガス、溶接用・産業用及び医療用機器の各種製品の供給を通じて、お客様の事業活動に貢献している会社です。</dd>\n          </dl>\n\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-3\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 offset-md-0 col-8 offset-2\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/qa01.png\" alt=\"第一開明って何の会社なの？\" class=\"img-fluid\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"row mt-sm-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-9 order-md-2\">\n          <dl>\n            <dt class=\"qa_tit tit_space_s\">Ｑ：第一開明の仕事内容は？</dt>\n            <dd class=\"faq_dd\">主な仕事として、配送・営業、充填・容器検査、技術（エンジニアリング）、業務（事務）に分類されます。</dd>\n          </dl>\n        </div>\n\n\n\n        <div class=\"col-md-3 order-md-1\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 offset-md-0 col-8 offset-2\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/qa02.png\" alt=\"第一開明の仕事内容は？\" class=\"img-fluid\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </article>\n\n    <div class=\"contents_space\">\n      <h3 class=\"tit_border sub_tit mb-3\">配送・営業</h3>\n      <div class=\"row\">\n\n        <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-2\">\n          <div class=\"row row-10\">\n            <div class=\"col-6\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img01.jpg\" alt=\"配送・営業\" class=\"img-fluid\"style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-6\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img01_2.jpg\" alt=\"配送・営業\" class=\"img-fluid tb_mb15\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-1\">\n          <p>お客様へ産業用・医療用ガス、関連機器機材等の納入やお困り事への企画・提案を行います。</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 offset-md-2 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=graduate&work=delivery-sales\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この新卒採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=career&work=delivery-sales\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この中途採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"contents_space_s\">\n      <h3 class=\"tit_border sub_tit mb-3\">充填・容器検査</h3>\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-2\">\n          <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img04_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n          <div class=\"row row-10\">\n            <div class=\"col-6\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img02_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-6\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img03_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid tb_mb15\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-1\">\n          <p class=\"mb-3\">高圧ガス容器にガスの充填と容器検査を行います。容器には使用できる期間が定められており、期間の過ぎた容器は耐圧検査することにより、再利用できます。</p>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 offset-md-2 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=graduate&work=filling-inspection\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この新卒採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=career&work=filling-inspection\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この中途採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"contents_space_s\">\n      <h3 class=\"tit_border sub_tit mb-3\">技術（エンジニアリング）</h3>\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-2\">\n          <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n          <div class=\"row row-10\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 pb-4\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img06.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 pb-4\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/img07.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid tb_mb15\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-1\">\n          <p class=\"\">ガス配管設備の設計・施工管理・メンテナンスまで一貫して携わります、各種点検作業も実施します。</p>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 offset-md-2 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=graduate&work=engineering\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この新卒採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=career&work=engineering\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この中途採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contents_space_s\">\n      <h3 class=\"tit_border sub_tit mb-3\">業務（事務）</h3>\n      <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-2\">\n          <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/recruit-img_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n          <div class=\"row row-10\">\n            <div class=\"col-6\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/recruit-img_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-6\">\n              <img src=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/dir/wp-content/themes/dkaimei/img/recruit/recruit-img_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid tb_mb15\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-6 order-md-1\">\n          <p class=\"\">売上入力、納品書・請求書発行や伝票処理、受注発注などの営業サポートと、電話・来客対応、パソコン入力や入出金処理などの営業所業務を行います。</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 offset-md-2 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=graduate&work=clerk\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この新卒採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 mb-2 mb-md-0\">\n          <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/?recruit_category=career&work=clerk\" class=\"button common_button\">\n            <span class=\"arrow_button\">この中途採用情報を見る</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"contents_nav_box\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"contents_nav\">\n      <ul class=\"row no-gutters\">\n        <li class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n          <span class=\"arrow_button active\">\n            <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/recruit/\"><i class=\"fas fa-building\"></i>採用情報</a>\n          </span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n          <span class=\"arrow_button\">\n            <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/recruit/graduate/\"><i class=\"fas fa-user-tie\"></i>採用情報（新卒）</a>\n          </span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n          <span class=\"arrow_button\">\n            <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/recruit/career/\"><i class=\"fas fa-clipboard-check\"></i>採用情報（中途）</a>\n          </span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n          <span class=\"arrow_button\">\n            <a href=\"https://dkaimei.jp.nipponsanso.com/intervi